  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is designed to evaluate medium-term central venous catheter placement in infants
      undergoing complex cardiac surgery using a new technique. This technique involves placement
      of the catheter into the inferior vena cava through a subcutaneous tunnel and through a
      tunnel between pericardium and diaphragm.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
